Class DeliveryService

java.lang.Object
businesslogic.DeliveryService
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDeliveryServiceProcessing
public class DeliveryService extends Object implements IDeliveryServiceProcessing
Contains the logic for dealing with admin and client operations - Plays the role of an observer using the Java PropertyChangeListener implementation - Singleton
